Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:14.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂  能听到吗{\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:20.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}狰狞无比的凄惨之战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爱总是无法无天的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:29.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:42.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这份心情无法释怀  无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:47.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}越是想着不可以  就陷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:52.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}变得连自己都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:56.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不如相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:00.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都决定要伴随在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:04.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:15.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}命运要我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要我止步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这理由却还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:29.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可为你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}狰狞无比的凄惨之战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爱总是无法无天的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
