Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩凑一起有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我散步时偶然经过这公寓前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前连聊天都顾不上  所以我就来看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这个  我做了些饼干  你不嫌弃的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妈妈做了纸杯蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是失败作  分你一些也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟父母相处得挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母都对我很温柔  亲人真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我给你们冲茶  进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱  实咲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  你们俩连休息日也这么热心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们送了些点心来  大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是遗物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我鉴定的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一会再慢慢查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我自己吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LIAR…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「骗子」的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是英语圈的城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们被吸进了那画里面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我应该是在龙司君的家里的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是梦？是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是现实哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像被带进了刚才的画里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和龙司的周围经常会有奇怪的事发生  不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我会找到回去的方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你就相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  龙司一定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先找出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实咲  要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连人影都没  幽灵城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逛了一下才发现  这城市好像在哪见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是前段时间看的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通的恐怖片啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美国的一个小城镇里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子们被杀人狂追杀的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人狂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低成本片  杀人狂也只是化装下拿个斧头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就正好像那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用  逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲进那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  刚才还开着的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子  那里有屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  快来救我们啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不管用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由有很多假设
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇安卡？！你什么时候进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢我  有难大家帮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One for all  All for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你这话有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是诅咒遗物的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过似乎有着一些特殊的规律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像也没人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有电？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道  要是能顺便找到些武器就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那男人是什么  必须想点对抗手段才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子  这有楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都走到这了可能我这话有点多余
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在恐怖片里一般去地下室肯定没好下场的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能找到一些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是恐怖片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这是梦？还是现实？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在恐怖片里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你就祈祷是个好结局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这照片是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心  而且低级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过脱困的关键一般都会在这种地方  找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最重要的回忆是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说  最重要的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候  床上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  实咲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Activity的数值很低
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这不是攻击型而是对接近的人起反应的陷阱型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且从状况可以判断出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XX染色体  也就是对女性起反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然舞台是对方的画布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么遗物的能力很可能会被无效化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的那匕首一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那镜子  要是对它说谎的话就会变成照片里的女孩一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成照片会怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不能再出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就见不到龙司了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我的提问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我的提问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说心里话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能为谁而死？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止最让你后悔的是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的回忆是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  回答我  回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能为谁而死？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？没有为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随时可以为龙司而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说  至今为止最让你后悔的是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三年前  带龙司去古董店的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司在那被恶性的诅咒遗物侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使力量暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因此有些伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他更受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼了很长一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说后悔的话这就是后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他和我都已经看开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会一直被诅咒遗物束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的回忆是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司…君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实咲  说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的回忆是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟龙司相遇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最爱的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司龙司龙司…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…龙司  最喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎  说谎  不可能有女人会说真话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人全是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住这画捕捉女性的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是与外界连接的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就可以救出她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画对我起反应的时候就是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我一定会救大家出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇安卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司龙司龙司…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画好像是被恋人背叛的罪犯所画的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此他才那么执着于谎言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真实才是脱困的关键啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便接下来的委托  竟然这么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏有龙司在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要故意无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的这事就要算你欠我的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你没说真话的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就没法从那房间出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…真话说的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘  秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是大家都喜欢龙司的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是模范的好结局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要是恐怖片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会在这再…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想太多了吧
